nodes.text: A Human was the assistant manager of a cantina called the Wookiee's Codpiece on the planet Nim Drovis. In 13 ABY, the protocol droid C-3PO auditioned to perform music at the Wookiee's Codpiece. Once the assistant manager heard the droid playback songs from his memory core, the Human rejected C-3PO and compared him to a festering jizz-box akin to one the Wookiee's Codpiece already possessed.
The assistant manager was briefly mentioned in Planet of Twilight, a 1997 novel by Barbara Hambly.
